---
title: Spicy Chipotle-Chorizo Flatbreads with Caramelized Onions and Jalapeños
description: A little smoky, sweet and spicy action is the name of the game for this super simple flatbread recipe. Chipotle sauce provides the perfect sauce base, while the caramelized onions give a gentle sweetness to offset the heat from the jalapeños. A crisp side salad helps lighten the palate!
